Package: polyIBD
Type: Package
Title: polyIBD: Inferring blocks of identity by descent between polyclonal samples using unphased haplotype data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Nicholas F. Brazeau <nbrazeau@unc.med.edu> [aut, cre]", 
    "Robert Verity <r.verity@imperial.ac.uk> [aut]"
  ))
Description: Using unphased genotypic data, we infer blocks of IBD between polyclonal samples. Written with malaria genomes in mind.  
